			Profile
			
			Dr.BaofengHuoisZhejiangUniversityLeadingProfessorofLiberalArts,ProfessorofOperationsManagementattheSchoolofManagement,ZhejiangUniversity,Co-DirectorofInstituteofSupplyChainManagement,DirectorofInstituteofSupplyChainQualityManagement,NewCenturyExcellentTalentofMOEofChina,&ldquo;DistinguishedYoungScholarofNaturalSciences&rdquo;and&ldquo;ZhijiangYoungScholarofSocialSciences&rdquo;ofZhejiangProvince,AssociateEditorofJournalofOperationsManagement.HereceivedhisPh.D.inoperationsmanagementfromTheChineseUniversityofHongKong,hisM.E.inManagementSciencesandEngineeringandB.E.inManagementInformationSystemsfromTianjinUniversity.BeforejoiningZhejiangUniversity,heworkedatXi&rsquo;anJiaotongUniversityandTheChineseUniversityofHongKong.
&nbsp;
Dr.Huo&rsquo;steachinginterestsareoperationsmanagement,logisticsandsupplychainmanagement,empiricalresearchmethods,andstructuralequationmodeling,etc.Hisresearchinterestsarelogisticsandsupplychainmanagement,relationshipmanagement,cross-culturaloperationsmanagement,etc.Hisresearchhaswonseveralbestpaperawards,includingTop-25Most-accessed&nbsp;Dissertation(ProQuest,2014),BestSupplyChainIntegrationandRelationshipManagementPaperAward(ICOSCM,2012),TheChina&rsquo;s100MostInfluentialInternationalPapers(InstituteofScientificandTechnicalInformationofChina,2011),Li&amp;FungBestPaperAward(ICOSCM,2011),BestApplicationResearchPaperAward(DecisionSciencesInstitute,2010),BestOperations/ManufacturingStrategyandPracticesPaperAward(ICOSCM,2009),DistinguishedSupplyChainManagementPaperAward(DecisionSciencesInstitute,2008)andChanHahnAward(AcademyofManagement,2007).
&nbsp;
HisresearchhasbeenpublishedoracceptedinrefereedjournalsincludingtheJournalofOperationsManagement(All3papersareTop25mostlycitedJOMpapers,andcitedbyHighlyCitedPapersofEssentialScienceIndicators(ESI),ProductionandOperationsManagement,InternationalJournalofProductionResearch,IEEETransactionsonEngineeringManagement,InternationalJournalofOperationsandProductionManagement,InternationalJournalofProductionEconomics,Information&amp;Management,SupplyChainManagement,IndustrialManagement&amp;DataSystems,InternationalJournalofPhysicalDistribution&amp;LogisticsManagement,BusinessHorizons,andotherjournals.Hisseveralpaperspublishedinthepastseveralyearshavebeencitedbymorethan1500articles,andmorethan500SCI/SSCIindexedjournalpapers.Hewas2014MostCitedChineseResearchersinBusiness,ManagementandAccountingofElsevier.
&nbsp;
HereviewsprojectsforHK-RGC,NNFCprojects,andreviewspapersforJournalofOperationsManagement,DecisionSciences,ProductionandOperationsManagement,JournalofSupplyChainManagement,JournalofBusinessLogistics,EuropeanJournalofOperationalResearch,TransportationResearch，InternationalJournalofProductionEconomics,Omega,Asia-PacificJournalofManagement,DecisionSupportSystems,ManagementandOrganizationReview,SupplyChainManagement:AnInternationalJournal,InternationalJournalofPhysicalDistribution&amp;LogisticsManagement,etc.Hehasattendedseveralinfluencingglobalcooperativeresearchprojects,NNFCandMOEofChinaprojectsastheleaderortheteammember.
			
				
